high_descs: Turn left to reach the passage and turn left to walk to the end of the passage and turn right to reach the diningtable.
Pick up the banana on the left from the table.
Head to the sidetable with the microwave on the right.
Put the banana on the sidetable.
Turn right to head back to the diningtable.
Pick up the banana from the table.
Head to the sidetable with the microwave on the right.
Put the banana on the sidetable next to the other banana.
anns.task_desc: Put two bananas on the SideTable.

high_descs: Leave the diningtable. Turn left. Go straight ahead. When you enter the diningtable, turn right. Then turn left to be in front of the diningtable.
Take the banana.
Cross to the right, go to the sidetable. Turn right until you have the microwave in front of you.
Place the banana on the sidetable to the left.
Return to the diningtable.
Take the banana.
Back to the microwave sidetable.
Place the banana next to the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Search for two bananas. Place them on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn left and exit this room, then left again into the next room, approaching the white diningtable ahead.
Pick up the banana on the left, on top of the scattered objects.
Turn right and head towards the sidetable.
Place the banana down on the sidetable in front of the microwave.
Return to the white diningtable.
Pick up the second banana from the table.
Return to the sidetable with the microwave.
Put the second banana down next to the first banana on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put two bananas down on a SideTable with a microwave.
